# Affiliate SEO

## Per-page requirements

- Unique title tag (50-60 chars) with primary keyword near front
- Meta description (150-160 chars) with keyword and value prop
- Exactly one H1 per page
- Primary keyword in first 100 words
- JSON-LD schema via `SEOHead` (Product/Review or ItemList)
- Canonical URL set
- 2+ internal links to related cluster pages where available

## Avoid

- Keyword stuffing
- Duplicate titles across pages
- Thin roundup content under 800 words
- Multiple H1 tags

## After publish

Update article `status: published` in `seo/affiliate-keywords.yaml`.
